和經歷。透過與這些水晶共同作用，個人可以更好地了解自己，並體驗個人成長。</p></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-fbWUsZ educRc pf-147_"><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-148_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-149_"><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-150_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">這些水晶有助於建立內在和關係的連結，尋找平衡。它們協助恢復和諧，平衡具有挑戰性的情況。透過與這些水晶共同作用，個人可以在不平衡中前進，並為個人成長創造一個支持和滋養的環境。</p></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-fbWUsZ educRc pf-152_"><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-153_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-154_"><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-155_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">它們具有平衡的雙面形狀，沒有固定的比例，表現出變化性。這些水晶有助於吸收能量，減輕自我懷疑，並提供保護。它們幫助個人克服自我否定的感覺，真實地生活，擺脫懷疑的陰影。透過與這些水晶共同作用，個人能夠擁抱自己真正的潛力。</p></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-fbWUsZ educRc pf-157_"><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-158_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-159_"><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-160_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">這些水晶擁有微觀上難以區分的微小晶體，具有平靜穩定的影響力，它們幫助個人找到內在的平靜，減少不耐煩，促進情緒的療癒和平衡。
</p></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-fbWUsZ educRc pf-162_"><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-163_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-164_"><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-165_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">憑藉其非晶體無定形結構，它們代表著轉變和重生，與經歷重大人生變化的個人產生共鳴，為過渡期提供支持，並利用不可預測的高能量促進個人成長和自我探索。</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-crHmcD jDvJAM pf-167_"><button type="button" class="sc-jrQzAO eqVTRu pf-168_ pf-bg-lazy pf-anchor" data-header-id="1144bd5c-c895-4ab8-958c-da67f106ffa2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><span>4 - 晶石顏色與療癒能量
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="1144bd5c-c895-4ab8-958c-da67f106ffa2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-kDTinF dTimTh pf-170_"><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-171_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-172_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-emDsmM BOtMC pf-173_">充滿活力的晶石療癒能量調色盤</h3></div></div></div><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-175_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-176_"><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-177_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">顏色在水晶療癒領域起著至關重要的作用。 各種顏色的光具有不同的能量強度，可以深刻影響我們的身心健康，改變我們的思想和感知。 我們對不同顏色的本能和不自覺的反應說明了不同色調的晶體如何以獨特而強大的方式與我們產生共鳴。每種顏色的光對應於特定的波長頻率，通過我們的眼睛傳輸到大腦。 這些電磁波攜帶與我們的能量系統相互作用的獨特振動磁場。 因此，不同顏色的水晶可以影響我們的能量並帶來不同的療癒效果。</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-179_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-180_"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0631/8535/4990/files/4_-_The_Vibrant_Palette_of_Crystal_Healing_Energies_500x.jpg?v=1685584626" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0631/8535/4990/files/4_-_The_Vibrant_Palette_of_Crystal_Healing_Energies.jpg?v=1685584626 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0631/8535/4990/files/4_-_The_Vibrant_Palette_of_Crystal_Healing_Energies_1000x.jpg?v=1685584626 768w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0631/8535/4990/files/4_-_The_Vibrant_Palette_of_Crystal_Healing_Energies_500x.jpg?v=1685584626 320w" width="1080" height="400" sizes="(min-width: 1536px) 1536px, (min-width: 1024px) 1280px, (min-width: 640px) 768px, 320px" loading="lazy" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-leSONj uTJGF pf-181_"/></div></div></div><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-182_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-183_"><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-184_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">了解晶體顏色的重要性使我們能夠利用它們獨特的振動並選擇合適的晶體來支持我們的意圖和身心。 無論您尋求平靜、活力、清晰還是情緒平衡，探索水晶的不同顏色都會打開一個充滿療癒可能性的世界。</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-186_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-187_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-emDsmM BOtMC pf-188_"><i class="sc-hWBuOZ iKxntp pf-189_ pfa pfa-circle" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><b>BLACK</b></h3><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-190_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Grounding, Protection, Exorcism, Cleansing</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-192_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-emDsmM BOtMC pf-193_"><i class="sc-hWBuOZ iKxntp pf-194_ pfa pfa-circle" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><b>BROWN</b></h3><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-195_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Adaptability, Stability, Support</p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-md:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-eySxxw fIKYYX pf-197_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-emDsmM BOtMC pf-198_"><i class="sc-hWBuOZ iKxntp pf-199_ pfa pfa-circle" data-pf-type="Icon"></i><b>&nbsp; RED</b></h3><p class="sc-bvFjSx yVjXo pf-200_" tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Vitality, Enthusiasm, Health, Strength, Instinct</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-iAKWXU lesjfG pf-202_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--